graphics.name: Amino sugar and nucleotide sugar metabolism

nodes.name: L-aspartate:ammonia ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Aspartate + Ammonia <=> AMP + Diphosphate + L-Asparagine

nodes.name: L-aspartate:L-glutamine amido-ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Aspartate + L-Glutamine + H2O <=> AMP + Diphosphate + L-Asparagine + L-Glutamate

nodes.name: L-Aspartic acid:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Aspartate + H2O + Oxygen <=> Oxaloacetate + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: L-Aspartic acid:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Aspartate + H2O + Oxygen <=> Oxaloacetate + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: D-Aspartate:oxygen oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: D-Aspartate + H2O + Oxygen <=> Oxaloacetate + Ammonia + Hydrogen peroxide

nodes.name: L-Citrulline:L-aspartate ligase (AMP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Citrulline + L-Aspartate <=> AMP + Diphosphate + N-(L-Arginino)succinate

nodes.name: IMP:L-aspartate ligase (GDP-forming)
nodes.rxn: GTP + IMP + L-Aspartate <=> GDP + Orthophosphate + N6-(1,2-Dicarboxyethyl)-AMP

nodes.name: L-alanine:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Alanine + NAD+ + H2O <=> Pyruvate + Ammonia + NADH + H+

nodes.name: succinate-semialdehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Succinate semialdehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Succinate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: succinate-semialdehyde:NAD+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Succinate semialdehyde + NAD+ + H2O <=> Succinate + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-glutamate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Glutamate + NAD+ + H2O <=> 2-Oxoglutarate + Ammonia + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-glutamate:NAD+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Glutamate + NAD+ + H2O <=> 2-Oxoglutarate + Ammonia + NADH + H+

nodes.name: L-glutamate:NADP+ oxidoreductase (deaminating)
nodes.rxn: L-Glutamate + NADP+ + H2O <=> 2-Oxoglutarate + Ammonia + NADPH + H+

nodes.name: L-Glutamate:ammonia ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + L-Glutamate + Ammonia <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + L-Glutamine

nodes.name: HCO3-:L-glutamine amido-ligase (ADP-forming, carbamate-phosphorylating)
nodes.rxn: 2 ATP + L-Glutamine + HCO3- + H2O <=> 2 ADP + Orthophosphate + L-Glutamate + Carbamoyl phosphate

nodes.name: Carbon-dioxide:ammonia ligase (ADP-forming,carbamate-phosphorylating)
nodes.rxn: 2 ATP + Ammonia + CO2 + H2O <=> 2 ADP + Orthophosphate + Carbamoyl phosphate

nodes.name: succinate-semialdehyde:NADP+ oxidoreductase
nodes.rxn: Succinate semialdehyde + NADP+ + H2O <=> Succinate + NADPH + H+

nodes.name: N-acetyl-L-aspartate:L-glutamate ligase (ADP, N-acetyl-L-aspartyl-L-glutamate-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + N-Acetyl-L-aspartate + L-Glutamate <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + N-Acetylaspartylglutamate

nodes.name: N-acetyl-L-aspartyl-L-glutamate:L-glutamate ligase (ADP, N-acetyl-L-aspartyl-L-glutamyl-L-glutamate-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + N-Acetylaspartylglutamate + L-Glutamate <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + N-Acetylaspartylglutamylglutamate

nodes.name: citrate:L-glutamate ligase (ADP-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + Citrate + L-Glutamate <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + beta-Citryl-L-glutamate

nodes.name: N-acetyl-L-aspartate:L-glutamate ligase (ADP, N-acetyl-L-aspartyl-L-glutamate-forming)
nodes.rxn: ATP + N-Acetyl-L-aspartate + L-Glutamate <=> ADP + Orthophosphate + N-Acetylaspartylglutamate
